This paper focuses on wireless communication for UAVs, which involves networked systems and robotics (cs.NI and cs.RO). The proposed algorithm also uses a hybrid deep learning model, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of on-board sensors, which could involve computer vision (cs.CV) techniques.
